Follow link and add html inside textarea, add the below
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html>
<myhtml>
<p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" id="UploadIframe" data-attr="5" data-attr-url="uploadpageUrl"></p>
</myhtml>
</html>
